---
title: Caesar-Spiced Salmon with Creamy Caesar Salad
description: All the fun of Sunday brunch but for dinner! Caesar-spiced salmon gets a zippy, crunchy side of baby spinach, tomatoes and DIY croutons, dressed in a creamy, dreamy Caesar.
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/saumon-a-la-cesar-f5c23eb5.jpg
